metadata.description:
Artist, producer, and DJ Pauline Herr blesses us with a transcendent new track, “Nirvana.” Deftly balanced by melodic bliss and the tempered anticipation of the drop as the bass patiently builds, “Nirvana” mesmerizes. Massaging the brain like an expansive mind approaching enlightenment, the track opens up as if to usher listeners to a new dimension.

----

This is the eleventh track from HIGH FREQUENCY Volume 1—a compilation album curated by NOISE.

Read interviews with each artist at noisedao.mirror.xyz.
metadata.name: Pauline Herr - Nirvana #1
